OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FTim Burgess has remembered his friend
OL,8,FGary "Mani" Mounfield, saying "the
OL,9,Fworld misses him", as stars arrived on
OL,10,Fthe red carpet ahead of the Brit
OL,11,FAwards 2026.
OL,13,FMounfield, who was an original member
OL,14,Fof Manchester rock band The Stone
OL,15,FRoses, died at the age of 63 in
OL,16,FNovember 2025.
OL,18,FBurgess, best known as the frontman of
OL,19,FThe Charlatans, will pay tribute to
OL,20,FMounfield during the In Memoriam
OL,21,Fsection of the awards ceremony.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@KO]pD@_OUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
