CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FThe 58-year-old musician said: "When I
OL,8,Fwas asked (to pay tribute to
OL,9,FMounfield), it was obviously an honour.
OL,11,F"The world misses him, and the
OL,12,Fshockwaves seem to continue.
OL,14,F"And then the realisation of just how
OL,15,Fmuch The Stone Roses meant to
OL,16,Feverybody."
OL,18,FHe added: "I won't be saying anything
OL,19,Fmore than people already know, but
OL,20,FI'll just be reaffirming it on this
OL,21,Fstage."
OL,26,@oD@`OUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@KO]zD@KOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
