PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FBurgess also reflected on the awards
OL,8,Fceremony being held in Manchester for
OL,9,Fthe first time, after nearly 50 years
OL,10,Fin London.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think it's cool to not be
OL,13,Fin London, because music is kind of
OL,14,Feverywhere.
OL,16,F"There's been amazing bands from
OL,17,FSheffield, Glasgow, Edinburgh, amazing
OL,18,Fbands from Liverpool, Manchester. It's
OL,19,Fgreat."
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
