PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FHappy Mondays frontman Shaun Ryder was
OL,8,Falso among the stars who paid tribute
OL,9,Fto Mounfield on the red carpet.
OL,11,F"Mani was a beautiful human being, an
OL,12,Fabsolutely beautiful human being," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Never mind being a genius bass
OL,16,Fplayer, he was just a really beautiful
OL,17,Fperson. I've never seen him be unkind
OL,18,Fto anybody."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
