OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FThe singer, from Greater Manchester,
OL,8,Falso said he thinks it is "brilliant"
OL,9,Fthat the award ceremony is being held
OL,10,Fin the North West for the first time.
OL,12,FArtists including Tallia Storm and US
OL,13,Fsingers Alex Warren and Ashley Roberts
OL,14,Fwere also among the early arrivals on
OL,15,Fthe red carpet at Manchester's Co-Op
OL,16,FLive arena.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@eO]
