OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FIt comes three years after his last
OL,8,Fperformance on the Brits stage at the
OL,9,Fawards in 2023, which saw him take
OL,10,Fhome four gongs following the release
OL,11,Fof his album Harry's House.
OL,13,FDean, 26, is nominated for artist and
OL,14,Falbum of the year, pop act, and has
OL,15,Ftwo chances at winning song of the
OL,16,Fyear for Man I Need and Rein Me In,
OL,17,Fthe latter thanks to a guest spot with
OL,18,FSam Fender.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FYoung, 25, is up for best pop act,
OL,8,Fartist of the year, breakthrough act,
OL,9,Fbest alternative and rock act and best
OL,10,Fsong.
OL,12,FElsewhere, Britpop band Pulp have
OL,13,Fscored their first nomination in 30
OL,14,Fyears, in the best group category,
OL,15,Fwhile last year's Mercury Prize winner
OL,16,FFender has four nominations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
