PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FLily Allen, whose album West End Girl
OL,8,Fcaused a stir when it was released
OL,9,Flast year, is nominated in three
OL,10,Fcategories ` for best album, artist of
OL,11,Fthe year, and pop act.
OL,13,FSinger-songwriter Warren's Ordinary is
OL,14,Fcompeting with US pop stars including
OL,15,FTaylor Swift, Chappell Roan, Gracie
OL,16,FAbrams and Sabrina Carpenter in the
OL,17,Finternational song of the year
OL,18,Fcategory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
