PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772386497
OL,3,C'The world misses him': Tim Burgess
OL,4,Cremembers Stone Roses' Mani ahead of
OL,5,CBrits
OL,7,FAlso among the musical names
OL,8,Fperforming at the show are Dean and
OL,9,Fsinger-songwriter Raye as well as rock
OL,10,Fband Wolf Alice, Mark Ronson and
OL,11,FAmerican singer-songwriter Sombr,
OL,12,Fwhose real name is Shane Boose.
OL,14,FAdvance winners already announced
OL,15,Finclude Oasis's Noel Gallagher, who
OL,16,Fwill be named songwriter of the year,
OL,17,Fwhile record producer and DJ Ronson
OL,18,Fwill be honoured with the outstanding
OL,19,Fcontribution to music award.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
